elements.name: Create a new account in Pivotal Tracker

steps.name: I create a new account "New Account" in Pivotal Tracker
I should see the new account page
I navigate to Account page
I should see the new account in the Accounts page
I navigate to Dashboard page
I should see the new account in the Project Creation popup
I am logged in with Username and Password into the Pivotal Tracker

elements.name: Configure the account name of an account created

steps.name: I create a new account "New Account" in Pivotal Tracker
I configure the account Name "Change Name" and save the changes
I should see the new account page
I navigate to Account page
I should see the new account in the Accounts page
I am logged in with Username and Password into the Pivotal Tracker

elements.name: Delete a account in Pivotal Tracker

steps.name: I create a new account "New Account" in Pivotal Tracker
I enter to the Settings and delete the account with name "New Account"
I should see a yellow message "New Account was successfully deleted." in Accounts Page
I should see all of the accounts except the deleted account
I am logged in with Username and Password into the Pivotal Tracker
